        <h1><b> Consulting Services </b></h1>
        <img class="services_img" src="images/services_img_1.png" alt="Services">
            <p id="services-p"> 
                With a strong focus on supporting organizations in their technological evolution, EDST Consulting aims to be a trusted partner 
                in guiding you through the entire technology adoption and implementation process. From optimizing the design office to 
                streamlining operations on the shop floor, its experienced team brings expertise and insights to empower organizations in their 
                transformative journey.<br><br>
                EDST Consulting, a new business vertical of EDS Technologies, leverages the extensive 28 years of experience and 
                industry expertise of EDST. With a broad client base of more than 2000 customers spanning OEMs, suppliers, start-ups, 
                and businesses of various sizes, EDST has established itself as a prominent player in this niche segment. The 
                widespread recognition and accolades earned by EDST further solidify its position as a leading and trusted partner 
                for organizations seeking transformative solutions.
            </p>
            

        <h1><b> 3DEXPERIENCE Consulting Offerings </b></h1>
        <img class="services_img" src="images/services_img_2.png" alt="Services">
