                rapidly among manufacturing organizations in India and worldwide. EDST consulting can help you take full advantage 
                of this business platform and associated applications. This will be guided by the best practices, technology, and 
                methodology provided by EDST Consulting Division. <br><br>
                This enables cross-functional collaboration, navigate document repository and collaborative lifecycle management, 
